name: Street Dogs
description: Street Dogs ($StreetDogs) is a deflationary BEP20 token from Binance Smart Chain. A decentralized ecosystem that has USDT rewards for hourly investors. The token will be available for purchase on various crypto exchanges and will be tied to the value of the Binance smart chain. Street Dogs was created to simplify the use of blockchain technology to the point where it seems like a walk in the park. Street Dogs symbolizes the gateway to harnessing the potential that Web3 financial technology brings to change the world for the better, making it easier to use for everyone, like a walk in the park while all $StreetDogs holders automatically earn $Shib in each transaction.
